# Project-local rules

# AGENTS.md is the contributor / agent guide and is intentionally
# local-only: it documents the v0.5+ release workflow, the GPG
# signing setup, and the AI-agent operating rules for this
# specific host. Other contributors can write their own copy
# from scratch; we don't want to track the host-specific
# passphrase location, keygrip, and the v0.x release-tagging
# workflow in the shared repo.
AGENTS.md
ROADMAP.md
